## Testing

- Mock cloud clients at the boundary in unit tests.
- Reserve real GCP calls for explicit integration tests.

## Avoid

- Hard-coded project IDs, credentials, or service account keys.
- Assuming local ADC credentials exist in tests.
- Network access or credential checks while rendering generated skills.
- Cloud-specific code mixed into domain logic when a boundary would keep it
  testable.
